title: American horror story asylum - exorcism scene part 1
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment:
This is what the newer seasons are missing
Scenes that are hard to watch
“If you look in the face of evil, evil’s gonna look right back at you”
One of the best acted posessions in my opinion, he somehow makes his voice perfect for the role

Interesting how he killed a goat and ate  her heart. Kinda like the Butcher and Lee were offered boar's heart as a symbol of conversion and selling their souls to the old gods in Roanoke. I do feel like all seasons are connected... And I do think that the ''old gods'' are demonic deities.
After watching the whole season, well, I won't spoil it.  Some of the reactions can be read more deeply now is all.
